column5: Hello to everyone on OFC! Parryfish here. Im from Parrysound and live right on the water! Ill be joining the OFC tourny. Hope to meet new friends and fishing partners along the way! ..
Let me be the first to say, Its about time! Glad to see ya on here..tight lines my man!
Welcome to the board I joined not to long ago and it's a great site here a great bunch on this site.
Welcome to OFC PF !! This place is the Bee's Knees  Paul
Welcome to the board.  I'll have to remember to blow the horn when I'm passing by Parry Sound next month.
